cards.title: Anthony Casalena
cards.description: Anthony Casalena is the Founder and CEO of Squarespace, which launched in 2004.

cards.title: Nicole AnaSenes
cards.description: Nicole brings 20 years of technology industry experience to Squarespace’s Finance Team, and has spent much of her career building new or transforming existing businesses.

cards.title: Andrew Bartholomew
cards.description: As the leader of Squarespace's Strategy division, Andrew is responsible for developing the analytical frameworks that shape the company’s business.
